title: What's up with Deebo? Dolphins expectations; Mock Draft; NFL Prospect, Breece hall
itunes:title: What's up with Deebo? Dolphins expectations; Mock Draft; NFL Prospect, Breece hall
description:
The Good Morning Football Podcast begins with Deebo Samuel's trade request. Hosts Kay Adams, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager and Super Bowl Champion Shaun O'Hara explain why Deebo's trade request is odd and surprising. Then the GMFB crew shares their mock draft which includes two shocking names in the top-10. Later, they dive into the Miami Dolphins roster and realistic expectations for them and they finish up being joined by NFL draft prospect Breece Hall and he shares why he should be a first round pick and the first RB off the board in the NFL draft and he also talks about his successful collegiate career at Iowa State.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
